Legend
Z in dotted circle := pointer to the newest node
Z in solid circle := the dummy newest node
Y := a node being pushed as the newest.
"slice" := the slice to replace or delete.
K := the node directly newer than the slice.
J := the newest node included in the slice.
H := the oldest node included in the slice.
G := the node directlyÂ older than the slice.
R := the node to replace the slice with.
